  "description": "<p>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</p>\n<p>Responsibilities</p>\n<p>· Perform all massage and treatment correctly and professionally.</p>\n<p>· Consult with clients to identify appropriate treatments.</p>\n<p>· Set up work stations, and ensure cleanliness and tidiness throughout shift.</p>\n<p>· Assist to keep linens clean and tidy, and replacing them between sessions.</p>\n<p>· Keep documentation and maintain clients’ files</p>\n<p>· Comply with all applicable standards, rules and regulations.</p>\n<p>Requirement:</p>\n<p>• Able to work weekend and Public Holidays</p>\n<p>• Friendly and cheerful personality</p>\n<p>• Passion in reflexology and / or massage/ spa</p>\n<p>• Fair in customer service</p>",
